---
title: Shrimp Banh Mi Burger with Sriracha Mayo and Carrot Fries
description: Banh mi is a popular Vietnamese sandwich with a French flair. It’s traditionally made with crusty baguette, a hefty chunk of meat, pickled veggies, and spicy condiments. Our chefs didn’t mess with the veggies or the condiments, but they did swap out baguette for buttery brioche and meat for shrimp. It’s refreshingly light (especially with the carrot fries) but unbelievably satisfying.
